        content: `PODS will deliver the container to your driveway or another accessible location. You then load it on your own schedule over however many days you have. Pack heavy, large items at the back first and use furniture pads or moving blankets to protect surfaces. Stack boxes from floor to ceiling and fill empty spaces to prevent shifting during transport. You supply your own lock — PODS recommends a disc lock, which is more secure than a standard padlock.`,
        tip: `PODS sells packing supplies on their website and you can add them to your order. Alternatively, you can buy moving blankets and disc locks at hardware stores.`,
